The paper deals with language modeling tasks and deep learning models, which are typically associated with the categories of natural language processing (cs.CL), machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), neural and evolutionary computing (cs.NE), and computer vision and pattern recognition (cs.CV). The title of the paper also mentions "Question Answering Machines", which further supports the relevance of these categories. Among these categories, cs.CL is the most likely one, as it directly relates to language modeling tasks.
